n filled up with the answers that a given user has given.</li><li>The grid should have all filters enabled to be able to filter the result set by any of the bound fields.</li><li>Bellow it there should be an option to create  a query out of the survey result and bind it over the user dashboard.</li></ul><p><br></p>', CAST(N'2020-07-25T22:02:11.277' AS DateTime), CAST(N'2020-07-25T22:02:11.277' AS DateTime), 1, NULL, NULL, 15118, 1, 1005, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, N'48', N'48', N'', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, CAST(N'2020-07-25T22:02:11.277' AS DateTime), NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL)
